{"title":"NAC JAMA-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/NAC JAMA-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"NAC\\NJAMA 2024","guid":"VkeAcLAV3LPFHgf88EOldg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Resumen","guid":"U41L7QpYfFTzf7NJjvlzzg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Neumonía adquirida fuera del hospital.","guid":"mLDEqflKKR1tavCY2joKfQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• Excluye neumonía hospitalaria o asociada a ventilador.","guid":"sHBtssNdTq8XYuQhHY6nwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"2. Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• Visitas a urgencias: 1.4 millones/año (EE. UU.).","guid":"g-epsjsbBghPcT6le-hftQ","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• Hospitalizaciones: 740,000/año.","guid":"a5Vd8I0TepJzoEbwf_vMfQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"• Muertes: 41, 000/año (EE. UU.).","guid":"-ZDynYoVffMhgGWkKynWmw","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"• Incidencia hospitalaria: 24. 8/10,000 personas-año.","guid":"G8iF_X1E3g-NbHm35wiG0A","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"5","text":"•  65 años: Incidencia 63/10,000 personas-año.","guid":"G6Ggim1wY9KE3DfgQuUhqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"3. Factores de riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Edad >65 años.","guid":"RXj3HkBE9GJGj6jRaEZCag","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Enfermedad pulmonar subyacente.","guid":"DA4wowRwTEXi_kfkR2qAtA","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"• Tabaquismo.","guid":"PDq8r6zGAt-mCHAksYtexw","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"• Inmunosupresión.","guid":"14AzE6EA6v2OavucQ74mDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"1","text":"4. Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"1. Evaluación\\NDiagnóstica","guid":"FkFmEKpwOuzyPDHaV4gr2w","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Imagenología: Radiografía de tórax (primera línea).","guid":"H1BMIiiNGV7g32A2egrMcg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Pruebas virales: SARS-CoV-2 e influenza si prevalentes en la comunidad.","guid":"8xinXdjAefJMY_UOIMYHAQ","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"• Pruebas bacterianas (cultivos\\Nrespiratorios/sanguíneos):","guid":"IAI2J-LS-Pj4i7QyrRu_bw","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• Solo en CAP severa (uso de vasopresores, ventilación mecánica,\\N≥3 criterios menores de severidad).","guid":"9E-wJ4HZsW0byomvUUcPtQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"• O con factores de riesgo para MRSA o Pseudomonas.","guid":"r8Keq8hfrje7wlSPn6S00A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"16","text":"• ≥2 de los\\Nsiguientes","guid":"I1-9euhiCe1pvSh0r7IKlQ","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Fiebre (>38°C o <36°C), leucocitosis (>10,000/μL) o leucopenia (<4,000/μL).","guid":"u50k_TNN1wZN9D2k26xJbA","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• Síntomas: tos nueva o exacerbada, disnea.","guid":"l6RDxDZpdvYh8rwMuYq4qA","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"• Radiografía: infiltrados pulmonares (opacidades alveolares).","guid":"iTRI5o7o-YjyzuA63PZwzw","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"23","text":"• Pruebas virales: COVID-19, influenza.","guid":"vDeUjS1JhMamJbXG_Aw9ag","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"1","text":"5. Etiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"• Identificación del patógeno en 38% de hospitalizados.","guid":"54Qbf7cTQnG1cdPiPFbHog","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"• Principales\\Npatógenos:","guid":"sQpUztneVSLWQC8tYb8kGQ","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• S. pneumoniae: 15%.","guid":"FkyfLOjbRyoVBpqWbgFGSw","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• Virus: 40%.","guid":"4IhXcJKJLe1a48ZKgK7DQw","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"28","text":"2. Causas Comunes\\Nde CAP","guid":"QwDKQLhI7-Y0fm-O2h2SWA","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• Identificación de patógenos en 38% de los hospitalizados con CAP.","guid":"FtfvtvxVrjsPEKH8127Mrg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"• Patógenos virales: hasta 40% de los casos identificados.","guid":"Et9sJrXx6q7E4FSc1IdyrA","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"• Patógeno bacteriano más común: Streptococcus pneumoniae\\N(15% de los casos identificados).","guid":"TJJGl9nvDF2vAlguqlMnrQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"1","text":"6. Complicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Sepsis.","guid":"XoLTqW4B5AELjrA8Xayczw","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Síndrome de distrés respiratorio agudo (SDRA).","guid":"6B_1AS3Q-_kZTBy4s6lLIQ","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"• Muerte.","guid":"UlWmRNIxFgpSMpSF6VuJRA","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"1","text":"7. Tratamiento\\NEmpírico","guid":"zMdISIefG9rDrGwcyaroMg","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"3. Antibióticos para\\NTratamiento de CAP","guid":"ypswxos3YVNePoYaTpRtZg","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Ambulatorios sin\\Ncomorbilidades:","guid":"6rEq8umzSdkPEFa7AkqSMg","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• Amoxicilina 1g 3 veces/día o\\Ndoxiciclina 100 mg 2 veces/día.","guid":"HRP4ayx368Qsfo1cYq7T5w","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"• Ambulatorios con\\Ncomorbilidades:","guid":"2SEzr99h94-T9jPgfMdHjA","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• Terapia combinada: amoxicilina/clavulanato o\\Ncefalosporinas (ej. cefpodoxime, cefuroxima)\\N+ azitromicina.","guid":"RUTxT1ToTpEjRkXEe5P3lg","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"42","text":"• Hospitalizados (sin factores de riesgo\\Npara bacterias resistentes):","guid":"17UgXQKTtmTT4t9KfMiz1A","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Terapia combinada: β-lactámico (ej. ceftriaxona) +\\Nmacrólido (ej. azitromicina), mínimo 3 días.","guid":"ApJmRLMUkrV7ZmgSqQpkHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"42","text":"• CAP severa:","guid":"7oaUO0PXx39-CjD1Sg64XQ","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• Corticoides sistémicos + antibióticos empíricos según\\Nfactores de riesgo para bacterias resistentes.","guid":"fWi8gSoXFRfbt3PZSzPp5Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"41","text":"• Sin factores de riesgo de resistencia: β-lactámico + macrólido (ej. ceftriaxona + azitromicina).","guid":"wQmZS3TyS2n-DV3bm17KKA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"41","text":"• Duración mínima: 3 días.","guid":"x_4-eUgJzt5P3J2GZYuoow","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"41","text":"• Corticoides sistémicos en CAP grave: reducción de mortalidad a 28 días.","guid":"T3ETR1pQxFqLpHBdIzd7bA","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"1","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"bAmDOkJPEzwRtEji4d_W7w","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"1. Terapia\\NAntibacteriana\\NEmpírica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Ambulatorio:","guid":"LOHQQ0B9dUKaIMaORbIFlA","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"• Sin comorbilidades: amoxicilina o doxiciclina.","guid":"2DaX1bLLkIiiK_twfIvCqQ","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"• Con comorbilidades (EPOC, asplenia): amoxicilina/clavulanato o cefalosporina\\N(cefpodoxima, cefuroxima) + macrólido o doxiciclina.","guid":"c2tbSkJt5CeLc6hf8eFuuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"• Hospitalizado\\Nno severo:","guid":"eubKqh3IgA-jat3wkQSBdg","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"• β-lactámico (ampicilina + sulbactam o ceftriaxona) + macrólido.","guid":"qBMnD4chNCwaVv0-vPi24w","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"• Fluoroquinolona solo si alergia confirmada.","guid":"TdGBL_-DgJ17_c656MmlbQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"55","text":"• Hospitalizado\\Nsevero:","guid":"62DYUJ830hXsTikBtcbSoA","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"• β-lactámico + macrólido.","guid":"ChCArdJMiX1Yi7VuRVQRcA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"• Si no tolera macrólido → fluoroquinolona.","guid":"QvvrXYp1Krs2mu7NT6c1Tw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"54","text":"2. Cobertura\\NAnti-MRSA","guid":"9rnR_POm9oSliibwf_RP4A","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• Ambulatorio: No recomendada.","guid":"d8hOw12yiAvuiU5GXnPXgA","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"• Hospitalizado no severo: Solo si aislamiento\\Nrespiratorio previo de MRSA o resultados positivos.","guid":"J1_BXKkxOOakjBo4_0TnEw","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"• Hospitalizado severo: Con aislamiento respiratorio de MRSA o reciente hospitalización\\Ncon antibióticos parenterales → vancomicina o linezolid.","guid":"45wkULrYz-RC2Ena-GGMCw","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"54","text":"3. Cobertura\\NAntipseudomonal","guid":"","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Ambulatorio: No recomendada.","guid":"KEnazm5nNXZjsJKve2wNCA","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"• Hospitalizado no severo: Solo si aislamiento\\Nprevio de P. aeruginosa o cultivos positivos.","guid":"0CBNCQLcmIGdxE_c-aIq5A","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"• Hospitalizado severo: Con aislamiento de P. aeruginosa o reciente hospitalización con antibióticos parenterales\\N→ cefepime preferido, alternativas: ceftazidima, imipenem, meropenem.","guid":"n19g6vorHlYFxi8hQ24CuA","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"54","text":"4. Duración de\\NAntibióticos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Ambulatorio: 3 días.","guid":"WKWXSDidUdyW7jkhyAzJHw","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• Hospitalizado:","guid":"RQyTMYz0sZCrmh_MIpDHPQ","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"• 3 días si estable al día 3, 5\\Ndías si estable al día 5.","guid":"fOMt7WpV8fa-_ZQwH3cciQ","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"• ≥7 días si MRSA, Pseudomonas,\\Nempiema u otros patógenos inusuales.","guid":"3wmbTWYAryqkN3frIw0ILg","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"• Estabilidad a los 3 días: afebril (≤37.8°C), FC <100/min, FR <24/min,\\NSpO2 ≥90% o PaO2 ≥60 mmHg, PAS ≥90 mmHg.","guid":"A6kitUV-T06YMXs8piHdjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"54","text":"5. Transición a\\NTerapia Oral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Transición tan pronto el paciente mejore y pueda tolerar vía oral.","guid":"kh_eJxXpOLyfK07Pp945Lw","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"• Opciones: amoxicilina/clavulanato, cefpodoxima, cefuroxima, amoxicilina, azitromicina\\N(1500 mg total, incluyendo dosis IV).","guid":"4IJBBOaF0hFEV1Y6E1VIgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"54","text":"6. Uso de Esteroides","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Ambulatorio y hospitalizado no severo: No recomendados.","guid":"XFSGWXugDDJTSW9flYRNog","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Hospitalizado severo: Hidrocortisona 200 mg/día dentro de las primeras 24 h en CAP severa\\N→ ↓ mortalidad, ventilación mecánica, uso de vasopresores, estancia hospitalaria.","guid":"EiZU52B2lByBhWwTW1hApQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"54","text":"7. Prevención\\NSecundaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Vacunación: Neumococo, influenza, SARS-CoV-2, VRS.","guid":"CS2lLg-vYj_K4F_C2L4Egw","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"• Tabaquismo: Cese del tabaco, tratamiento de comorbilidades (EPOC, asma, IC).","guid":"YKKmyu-3K_3oeO-yX-q9ag","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"• Riesgo de aspiración: Evaluación y terapia de deglución, higiene oral adecuada, tratamiento de alcoholismo.","guid":"oMvD-ZnCQUy6Ootwbk5t6g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"1","text":"8. Pronóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Mortalidad a 30 días:","guid":"eukP9xeRBPjlH8hMIdPbHw","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"• <60 años: 2.8%.","guid":"CuFFWWRTfExc-jUHkjQAHw","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"•  60 años + comorbilidades: 26. 8%.","guid":"kD0qAM9fAzKbvsQqie-0ww","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"0","text":"Patogénesis","guid":"q5xNEVwjypkFHoqeUHekAw","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"1. Proceso\\NPatogénico","guid":"dVO7pj-69_c9BSCCWXfGuA","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"• Proliferación rápida de patógenos (bacterias, hongos o virus) en alveolos y vías aéreas pequeñas.","guid":"NLKaZDT7drw6W08OoL-M1Q","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"• ↘ Homeostasis pulmonar → inflamación local (disnea, tos, consolidación radiográfica) y sistémica (fiebre, fatiga, sepsis).","guid":"T_QMwH0LehddNsqmAFcUXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"93","text":"2. Transmisión\\NViral","guid":"cP32ROCxQaXGu6jVXou63g","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"• Virus respiratorios (SARS-CoV-2, etc.) → aerosol (<5 μm) → ingreso directo al tracto respiratorio bajo por inhalación.","guid":"BgmdfIV_M5Md-03gRlSLyQ","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"• No se propagan por gotas respiratorias breves o fómites.","guid":"26wdfDbSDLUbcdbJLDtgJg","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"93","text":"3. Microbioma\\NPulmonar","guid":"EqiAammq1WBTnou1oONDBw","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• Pulmones ≠ estériles en individuos sanos.","guid":"lYqYkZKyws2KUBCno1H60A","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"• Contienen bacterias viables (mayoría de origen orofaríngeo) → activas metabólicamente → regulan defensas inmunológicas.","guid":"ov37VbNlxG14F5ob_VU46g","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"• Neumonía bacteriana: desequilibrio del microbioma, emerge un patógeno dominante.","guid":"sox4MqPUoCsKE_aaE99_aw","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"• Factores que favorecen emergencia\\Nde patógeno dominante:","guid":"qqY6nws0cHfK6DuOyyXwIQ","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"• Infecciones virales precedentes.","guid":"QnHcscfQXtYJNmB-JvzBGw","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"• Aspiración de contenido faríngeo/gástrico.","guid":"GaZWq6efZV1DdcjnOQ5SDw","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"• Alteraciones inmunitarias locales (disfunción ciliar, alteración de macrófagos).","guid":"Uqv0hZS-FUHGcIA78g7tQg","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"104","text":"• Uso previo de antibióticos sistémicos → selección de organismos resistentes.","guid":"hLFi4ukwXOLgB2qPaX85Fg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"93","text":"4. Aspiración","guid":"","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"• Neumonía por aspiración: se pensaba causada por flora anaerobia\\N(Bacteroides, Fusobacterium).","guid":"HuEagliGh-2KnJQ_YkKomQ","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"• Estudios recientes: CAP y neumonía por aspiración no muestran diferencias significativas en patógenos.","guid":"ewE4tBtD4oVMdog5Wwct4Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"4Ok7uI-bzQQ89yc4L_IbWw","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"1. Factores\\Nde riesgo","guid":"k7-iIJOWb-IxVSRJWtG24A","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Edad >65 años (principal factor de riesgo).","guid":"mEjEoGIcZ1ukcL2etIU_xA","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Limpieza mucociliar alterada (ej. tabaquismo → aOR: 1.57; IC 95%: 1.12-2.77).","guid":"A9GuZLeLzlyTeSrEu0tEjQ","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"• Enfermedades pulmonares: EPOC (aOR: 1.99; IC 95%: 0.67-13.53), asma (aOR: 1. 71; IC 95%: 1.00-4.20).","guid":"GH7oBJfYORJ5CuzBIpEgdg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"• Mala salud oral (aOR: 2.78; IC 95%: 1.60-4.40).","guid":"V6wAmSTKUwhZAKjekbw8Fw","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"113","text":"• Estado nutricional deficiente (aOR: 6.14; IC 95%: 0.65-11.58).","guid":"BalR5uFZ9JOv22QchgdRAQ","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"113","text":"• Exposición ambiental (metales, polvo, humos).","guid":"rDPQMXu9nPqALfDX6_wXQQ","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"113","text":"• Terapia inmunosupresora (aOR: 3. 10; IC 95%: 1.27-15.13).","guid":"-upgJ1Vwh4D3ylUoCymdew","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"112","text":"2. Etiología y\\Ndiagnóstico","guid":"1N5YHwzcGcxU7_UiPGof1g","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• Identificación del patógeno en solo 38% de los pacientes hospitalizados.","guid":"3ZH440bp7cQfZy-zz36xgQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• S. pneumoniae → 15% de los casos con etiología identificada.","guid":"PRoSGif_dPOd6BpEF_ZsnQ","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"• Virus respiratorios identificados en 40% (ej. rinovirus 9%, influenza A/B 6%).","guid":"Wl729oJc-o1UsNtsxVprsg","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"112","text":"3. Severidad y\\Netiología","guid":"dCMdxEkHPRbEGJb2quLcaw","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• CAP severa (UCI): mayor prevalencia de etiología bacteriana\\N(19% en UCI vs 9% fuera de UCI).","guid":"yHI93h9kOgH65b7LYWVtFg","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Patógenos más frecuentes en UCI: S. pneumoniae, S. aureus, Enterobacteriaceae.","guid":"OAlBgvEUu9HY5S3fey9Kag","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"• CAP en ambulatorios/jóvenes: mayor probabilidad de infecciones virales o patógenos atípicos\\N(Chlamydia pneumoniae, Mycoplasma pneumoniae).","guid":"jpmwK6JjDDvmKRaSxTJEFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"112","text":"4. Variación geográfica y\\Nestacional","guid":"LHOUStCf6MdS5dPKv1FmLw","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"• Patógenos varían según región y estación (ej.\\Ncoccidioidomicosis en el suroeste de EE.UU.).","guid":"w3baqLVOvKv0K834co0QkQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"• Exposición a TB y neumonía por Pneumocystis en inmunocomprometidos.","guid":"JMo2LsIUB8pUE41GiT7V0g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"lGyBZP1mzVDFXGm_Z5F7Ww","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"1. Criterios Diagnósticos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"• ≥2 signos o\\Nsíntomas:","guid":"LZdY4D3mzy20TN9CFL523A","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"• Temperatura: >38°C o <36°C.","guid":"QMH4ZFdLsY9pqhNhhho3cQ","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"• Leucocitos: <4000/μL o >10, 000/μL.","guid":"FTVRg2pabAZM9f7WPGvuCw","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"• Síntomas respiratorios: tos nueva o exacerbada, disnea.","guid":"ebEqwSXGqX4Jh58Kpm0fbw","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"134","text":"• Hallazgos radiográficos: opacidades en espacios aéreos sin otra explicación alternativa.","guid":"Y8siYCjOPnVF6qUnZKEqPg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"132","text":"2. Síntomas Comunes (Prevalencia\\Nen hospitalizados con CAP)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"• Tos nueva o exacerbada: 86.5%.","guid":"lH5CWtOjRJPbc6OYnpvaAg","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"• Aumento en producción de esputo: 51.7%.","guid":"6BN3K5S1Erzl4OjGNpjFxw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"• Disnea: 79.8%.","guid":"dYt9FS4rNomfXHOY-O_Dkw","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"132","text":"3. Signos\\NClínicos","guid":"UudGKL7PMEdb0Mp_8_tbrA","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• Hipoxemia: 33.2%.","guid":"c01nALZXQbnFdLYkK3F65Q","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"• Hallazgos auscultatorios (egofonía, estertores): 58.6%.","guid":"cvjiPFiNDqhvhuMRC3JecQ","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"• Taquipnea (>20/min): 68.9%.","guid":"jVYO4wYJd6ZXFaSaymJlJg","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"• Fiebre (>38°C): 60%.","guid":"B6rKApnuLmPIeRPp3rFcfQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"132","text":"4. Evaluación\\NRadiológica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"• Radiografía de tórax: primera línea, sensibilidad 70% (16%-95%),\\Nespecificidad 55% (0%-94%).","guid":"GKcmqUimNj67KrqymhhSfQ","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"• Hallazgos típicos: opacidades en espacio aéreo (>95%), pero no específicas\\N(atelectasia, edema, neumonitis por aspiración).","guid":"pV8EPPnJZOmofyX5F7bC6Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"• Tomografía computada (TC) si la radiografía es negativa pero se sospecha CAP\\N(43.5% de las opacidades en TC no vistas en radiografía).","guid":"4dAbqhPAZ5tbWMZ-8Y7PTQ","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"148","text":"• Ecografía pulmonar: alta sensibilidad (95%) y especificidad (75%).","guid":"KSCHIZ2l8GxfhNEewWYTJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"132","text":"5. Diagnóstico\\NDiferencial","guid":"6MFRVe-oUfPSnCNJZTmNMQ","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Exacerbación de EPOC.","guid":"kKXd54pBgqyKKqi251lrSg","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"• Bronquitis aguda.","guid":"gmGNUNfDeSxHe-9_V0Z8vw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"• Neumonitis por aspiración.","guid":"FEqvtxV6RcwSebYSrIumtQ","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"153","text":"• Embolismo pulmonar.","guid":"hTufRFddFren1u1upo20Jw","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"153","text":"• Malignidad pulmonar (9.2% de pacientes ≥65 años con diagnóstico de neumonía).","guid":"8C5i3YLa1QKz4pjyKR86SQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"0","text":"Pruebas\\NDiagnósticas","guid":"Tyh7HSiXe7LTMFBe-dDdZg","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"1. Indicación de\\NPruebas Diagnósticas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"• No todos los pacientes con sospecha\\Nde CAP requieren pruebas diagnósticas.","guid":"zVSXIa6kjVnL9bJKGywo-w","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"• Considerar si el resultado de la prueba\\Nmodificará el manejo clínico.","guid":"aPZ6_FhJP_p6uSrjYySW8g","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"160","text":"• Beneficios de pruebas rápidas\\N(SARS-CoV-2, influenza):","guid":"6baYr7CaW5RI2YGIuJcTlQ","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"• ↘ Uso de antibióticos.","guid":"8LhKflofuduhTqOO_UnFLg","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"• ↘ Hospitalización, estancia hospitalaria.","guid":"CvX1RqakGw9aeBhBt2HdPA","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"• ↘ Costos sanitarios.","guid":"0RFJgGPuFWezzgUr1qNF0w","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"163","text":"• Mejora en control de infecciones.","guid":"qASzjclsuTpANmTYay3Ong","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"159","text":"2. Pruebas\\NVirales","guid":"z0uUa9aBaAN1S3dLBiB2oA","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"• Recomendado por la IDSA realizar pruebas de SARS-CoV-2\\Ne influenza durante periodos de transmisión comunitaria.","guid":"2eUn3gT5fLG3_drNKr5oLQ","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"• Pruebas para otros virus solo en casos seleccionados donde se\\Nmodifique la terapia o se pueda descontinuar antibióticos innecesarios.","guid":"TD25vZXj7nAnr544NJ2bFw","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"159","text":"3. Pruebas\\NEtiológicas","guid":"wJ9bVwSV9x5qLkLHLt3_fg","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"• Indicadas en:","guid":"cMPSdyhEARclI2JvMbdsmg","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• CAP severa (criterios de gravedad IDSA/ATS).","guid":"yAB0HNbe312Mntm8eFbq5g","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"• Factores de riesgo para MRSA o Pseudomonas aeruginosa.","guid":"QfUqcEtDzkOlj0sQdhQlHg","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"• Falta de respuesta a antibióticos típicos.","guid":"GZu6gSfLftIIQgGen6GInQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"• Factores de riesgo para MRSA\\Ny Pseudomonas:","guid":"N6Au917dQsLHpXOst-2gLQ","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"• Infección previa por MRSA o Pseudomonas.","guid":"SD8Mulr-D-ddUPBz4xDiew","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"• Hospitalización en los últimos 90 días con uso de antibióticos parenterales.","guid":"6KQTcENIZ-_oWL7OHiL2zQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"0","text":"Pruebas\\NDiagnósticas","guid":"AaRuObihbb9o5YJLQtrz8Q","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"1. Pruebas Recomendadas en la\\NMayoría de los Casos de CAP","guid":"","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"• Pruebas de COVID-19\\Ne Influenza:","guid":"lGftM_oVOW-FkZiDQSAUqQ","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"• Recomendadas por IDSA cuando los virus son comunes\\Nen la comunidad o hay exposición potencial.","guid":"41laJkaF5WOyf1XVe2xXcA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"• Beneficios: ↓ tiempo a diagnóstico, aislamiento adecuado, inicio temprano de\\Nantivirales, ↓ uso de antimicrobianos, ↓ hospitalización y estancia hospitalaria.","guid":"ErLdzekPkPGfGTJijfqKXA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"179","text":"2. Pruebas Recomendadas en CAP Severa o con\\NFactores de Riesgo para MRSA o Pseudomonas","guid":"O8OTNnsy40Ut5SaGnRL3Iw","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"• Cultivos de Sangre:","guid":"tpFst51jwaW9nZY5_V0G0A","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"• Recomendados en CAP severa o con factores de riesgo (MRSA,\\NPseudomonas), o en pacientes recibiendo tratamiento empírico.","guid":"Uicr-T38eDSAlUoEvuujWw","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"• Problemas: Rendimiento ↓ con uso previo de antibióticos;\\Nresultados falsos positivos en pacientes sin bacteremia.","guid":"Z-PYol0gIM5hv0MdQfY0IQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"184","text":"• Cultivo Respiratorio y\\NTinción de Gram:","guid":"sRFW2pYMnfTdnanj2LXw_Q","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"• Recomendado en CAP severa o con factores de riesgo\\N(MRSA, Pseudomonas).","guid":"va2XOMCcVqSOmyndDk9MbA","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"• Limitaciones: No todos los pacientes producen esputo de calidad,\\Nresultados lentos, algunos patógenos no detectados.","guid":"S2TEk9c_smTviUJ0tjMdSQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"184","text":"• Hisopado Nasal\\Npara MRSA:","guid":"0XR2JaHHPbeMvb66PPomwA","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"• Útil en CAP severa para suspender antibióticos anti-MRSA si es negativo\\N(99% valor predictivo negativo).","guid":"cTS-e5BjbmqMhjWEXkhgPg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"179","text":"3. Pruebas Recomendadas en CAP Severa\\Ny Usos Especiales","guid":"3qj6Qm2zXwqd7aTEWOQFqQ","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"• Antígeno Urinario\\Nde Legionella:","guid":"dHFBwOeHwTECc5s--QX9KA","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"• Recomendado en CAP severa, exposición\\Na Legionella, viajes o brotes.","guid":"FOh3Opuazg803OVQ5uOESA","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"• Procalcitonina:","guid":"91PSpWciuBsTDO5O6QFqdw","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• Recomendada para guiar el inicio o descontinuación de\\Nantibióticos en combinación con diagnósticos virales.","guid":"h1Eg4TFWdL_AJfLInX80tQ","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"• Utilidad: Buen valor predictivo negativo (98. 3% para niveles ≤0.1 ng/mL)\\Nen coinfección bacteriana con SARS-CoV-2.","guid":"uGYHg_jhxyT1nQjOQ1IdUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"199","parent":"193","text":"• Pruebas Virales Ampliadas\\N(COVID-19 e Influenza excluidos):","guid":"GmUMokg18IeSbhRxteDo5A","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"• Recomendadas en CAP severa para guiar\\Nantibióticos en combinación con procalcitonina.","guid":"k2DZNgHWQGcrgbi99ATZcw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"179","text":"4. Pruebas No Recomendadas en la\\NMayoría de los Casos de CAP","guid":"","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"• Pruebas Invasivas del\\NTracto Respiratorio Inferior:","guid":"EXPn5POZYI7YHD8l03pxfQ","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"• Solo se justifican en pacientes\\Nen ventilación mecánica.","guid":"fT5BDb2aq9WyDdUKgApwtg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"ZexghaLCsjcaO-h9PBVrJg","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"1. Decisión de\\Nhospitalización","guid":"","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"• Basada en juicio clínico y herramientas de decisión.","guid":"qIW-y9mpqFMKLM9r-cyFMg","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"• Pneumonia Severity\\NIndex (PSI):","guid":"K8DTzDZ9KWCAcOnm9P1SnA","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• Categorías I-V (V = peor).","guid":"LRm8jK34Yxp3VtWso7ghKg","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"• Predice mortalidad a 30 días.","guid":"rTr3RU-A9UOW_rYHEuQO4g","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"• PSI I-III (bajo riesgo) → manejo ambulatorio.","guid":"l4MxIeKXmM29vWiXRaTWvA","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"207","text":"• Considerar juicio clínico en pacientes jóvenes o con factores sociales\\N(ej. indigencia, uso de sustancias).","guid":"iWp93YyIYTaWdRX5hOu4yQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"204","text":"2. Terapia Antibacteriana\\NEmpírica","guid":"lTxMgwmle1qm2NKRV-CVbg","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"• Según severidad y patógeno\\Nprobable (guías ATS/IDSA 2019):","guid":"ftq2HVjZMXthXquMTIbCxA","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"• CAP no severa:","guid":"vtd9WNf1T0IRn5fKdUuevw","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"• β-lactámico (ej. ceftriaxona) + macrólido (ej. azitromicina)\\No monoterapia con fluoroquinolona (ej. levofloxacino).","guid":"vwwRaWhr9spu-K-XtiNdrA","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"• Fluoroquinolonas: evitar si es posible\\N(resistencia, C. difficile, ruptura de tendón).","guid":"c8hPSc2yNO6zCncT9cWavQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"213","text":"• CAP severa:","guid":"fK070DIv-jjP4RH_dO_s-Q","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"• Similar a no severa, pero con preferencia por\\Nfluoroquinolonas en caso de contraindicación a macrólidos.","guid":"ZxvFJgczPSl3GsPIKCy3kQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"204","text":"3. Terapia Anti-MRSA o\\NAntipseudomonal","guid":"","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"• Evaluar según\\Nfactores de riesgo:","guid":"jQUU-wA6bTH9RaoDhumjUg","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"• Infección previa por MRSA o Pseudomonas.","guid":"Gqvnz1Jb-7B01xgPEZAadQ","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"220","text":"• Hospitalización en últimos 90 días con antibióticos parenterales.","guid":"Ke4JUNwAGE0vUENx8_CLgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"219","text":"• MRSA: Suspender si test nasal es negativo\\N(99% valor predictivo negativo).","guid":"Gbm1TKi2JJkzL08VDY97CQ","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"219","text":"• Evitar terapia antibacteriana activa contra anaerobios (metronidazol, clindamicina)\\Npor riesgo de infecciones secundarias (C. difficile) y mortalidad aumentada (5%-6%).","guid":"4FyC2rmgcG9CkKo49Lrs_g","children":[]}]},{"id":"225","parent":"204","text":"4. Tratamiento en\\Npacientes ambulatorios","guid":"","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"• Sin comorbilidades: amoxicilina 1g 3 veces/día o doxiciclina 100 mg 2 veces/día.","guid":"TEbNteXe6XXqgfl-f5eQeA","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"225","text":"• Con comorbilidades: combinación de amoxicilina/clavulanato o cefalosporina + azitromicina.","guid":"BgwuTbP3_MIV783zqHrdqQ","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"225","text":"• Fluoroquinolonas solo si no se toleran las opciones de primera línea.","guid":"OL1Yy1t5ozfnyHqhnyEy5Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"204","text":"5. Coinfección bacteriana\\Ny COVID-19","guid":"KrbRDR63M7JwxlzTw-Zbyg","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"• Coinfección bacteriana en COVID-19 CAP es rara (3.5%).","guid":"BcDkcqbHKQ8zhveOMxWBBA","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"• Procalcitonina ≤0.1 ng/mL → 98. 3% valor predictivo negativo para coinfección bacteriana.","guid":"C4ABhSl0wRRukAOhQ_MCsA","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"• Procalcitonina >0.5 ng/mL → 9.3% valor predictivo positivo (coinfección bacteriana poco común).","guid":"OF7uVfYtq4Wi9E_q0mpovQ","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"229","text":"• Tratamiento antiviral para COVID-19 o influenza,\\Nantibióticos solo si se sospecha coinfección.","guid":"yVWQ7W1KPN18geGcjfItgA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"0","text":"Desescalada de\\NAntibióticos","guid":"L7NjhmWkAkRPVgmTiR94Mw","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"1. Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"• Desescalada antibacteriana\\N→ incluye:","guid":"4SZV8O9lnQKfdgikK3u0Ag","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"• Suspensión de antibióticos.","guid":"ncHJUBIQ3aVF1F75jQDZkA","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"236","text":"• Cambio de terapia empírica a dirigida.","guid":"Des5FTGmEa5sayZtP_34eg","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"236","text":"• Reducción de espectro terapéutico.","guid":"U5tk7tHRvDNbmMyan2fegw","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"236","text":"• Transición de terapia IV a oral.","guid":"GTcHvMHp2VUijhGYPorO6A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"241","parent":"234","text":"2. Transición IV a Oral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"• Realizar transición tan pronto el paciente pueda ingerir medicamentos orales.","guid":"AjZfGZFnHm_BV8Yp-cl0UQ","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"241","text":"• Ejemplo: CAP no severa → uso de orden predeterminada (IV inicial + cambio a oral)\\N↘ duración de antibióticos IV, menor costo.","guid":"TWxtBwswbzBQbbwx0EyNHw","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"241","text":"• Regímenes\\Norales comunes:","guid":"nSc-MkR0YEE8UH5ijXUpKw","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"• Amoxicilina/clavulanato o cefalosporinas orales (ej. cefpodoxime).","guid":"uTYdmX5OLtG-AOJZiPczEQ","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"244","text":"• Azitromicina (500 mg/día por 3 días o 500 mg día 1 y luego 250 mg/día por 4 días).","guid":"ZikFhRWrKF2nC5E9zkosqQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"247","parent":"234","text":"3. Reducción\\Ndel Espectro","guid":"","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"• Cambio de β-lactámico de amplio espectro (ej. ceftriaxona) a antibióticos más selectivos (ej. amoxicilina)\\N→ menor desarrollo de resistencia a gramnegativos.","guid":"VZejDPIvHoDLAen_wunu-A","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"247","text":"• S. pneumoniae es sensible a amoxicilina → opción adecuada en desescalada.","guid":"rNbdDTd0QKE2hom0y0WLBQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"234","text":"4. Duración Óptima\\Nde la Terapia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"• La duración óptima es desconocida,\\Npero estudios sugieren:","guid":"5rEXCO5XpYGdQRJWZsiCSw","children":[{"id":"252","parent":"251","text":"• CAP no severa en pacientes estabilizados al día 3 →\\N3 días de terapia β-lactámico es no inferior a 8 días.","guid":"AFj9XZGYtWBw1O1afF4C-Q","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"251","text":"• Duraciones prolongadas → mayor riesgo de efectos adversos\\N(infecciones secundarias, resistencia bacteriana).","guid":"h-pKMbGqejkb8_ptRujOJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"250","text":"• Terapia antibacteriana\\Nmínima recomendada:","guid":"hn0M5ZYaUmxKhpP3D7HHrA","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"• Pacientes ambulatorios sin CAP severa: 3 días.","guid":"5lGFyaUUSCwPcZOf_W5b5A","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"• Hospitalizados con CAP no severa estabilizados en 3 días:\\N3 días de tratamiento total.","guid":"fZdPNc0SrftbodWDsyfWdA","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"254","text":"• Pacientes que tarden >3 días en estabilizarse:\\N5 días de tratamiento total.","guid":"c2pkGUM649ZoJ_6vZ6w1fA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"258","parent":"234","text":"5. Complicaciones y\\NPatógenos Especiales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"• En casos de complicaciones (empiema) o infecciones por MRSA/Pseudomonas,\\Nse recomienda tratamiento de mayor duración (7 días o más).","guid":"8CnJyCuHpgM3rj93tvwTJg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"260","parent":"0","text":"Uso de Corticoides en Neumonía\\NAdquirida en la Comunidad (CAP)","guid":"IsI3CSTBzAWwT2iXUb2osQ","children":[{"id":"261","parent":"260","text":"1. Corticoides en\\NNeumonía por COVID-19","guid":"","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"• Evidencia del ensayo\\NRECOVERY (2020):","guid":"MhNIJV5Xc-w0KFQvpZFOnQ","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"• Dexametasona 6 mg diarios por 10 días.","guid":"aqK-ZS4EpgMLek_ed7ly2w","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"262","text":"• Reducción de\\Nmortalidad a 28 días:","guid":"uPRr9PIj1_tN9KVJAHauKg","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"• Sin dexametasona: 25.7%.","guid":"YSH7lotCtP_2U2QUIBSljw","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"264","text":"• Con dexametasona: 22.9%.","guid":"9wukI-wArlFxZDLo1AePYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"262","text":"• Beneficio mayor en\\Nventilación mecánica:","guid":"jA7gbkdjEFwKUf7rwX9YlQ","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"• Mortalidad a 28 días sin dexametasona: 41.4%.","guid":"pPk4j0oXYEL-Jr3R2M8Bqg","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"267","text":"• Con dexametasona: 29.3%.","guid":"aLlaP6NZF-cGyxGx_x8M6Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"270","parent":"260","text":"2. Corticoides en CAP\\Nsevera no COVID-19","guid":"","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"• Evidencia del ensayo\\NCAPE COD (2023):","guid":"IGTqxWUVMIRiJ5yoaX6LIg","children":[{"id":"272","parent":"271","text":"• Hidrocortisona 400 mg diarios, administrada dentro de las primeras 24 horas de severidad.","guid":"fTLzff_B4JcKvGe9eJDdfQ","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"271","text":"• Reducción de mortalidad a 28 días\\N(diferencia absoluta 5.6%):","guid":"KKd_wIrw34Ot6dSIY4C1SA","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"• Sin corticoides: 11.9%.","guid":"5kYFssjpvgVJkDSxERubNQ","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"273","text":"• Con corticoides: 6.2%.","guid":"G3zT_vZJ2__xNWtuuELBYA","children":[]}]},{"id":"276","parent":"271","text":"• Reducción en necesidad de ventilación mecánica,\\Nuso de vasopresores y estancia hospitalaria.","guid":"8TKHRoXpp-xHvP3i4diG6g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"277","parent":"260","text":"3. CAP No Severa","guid":"","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"• No se recomienda corticoides en CAP\\Nno severa sin indicaciones adicionales.","guid":"oxzhalAKnPniCPY6v7Q2kA","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"277","text":"• Riesgos de efectos adversos > beneficios en estos pacientes.","guid":"mYOki4YCYc2RtliI6Rb-6g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"280","parent":"0","text":"Prevención\\NSecundaria","guid":"C9gSCSTqcV3UA5Wdw7MvIg","children":[{"id":"281","parent":"280","text":"• Historia previa de CAP aumenta riesgo de recurrencia (OR: 1.86).","guid":"gV4xleeAMdqFBkoN7W_bFA","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"280","text":"• Intervenciones\\Npreventivas:","guid":"8vcutemN8J2CJELzhsPiUA","children":[{"id":"283","parent":"282","text":"• Cese de tabaquismo y alcohol.","guid":"6i-QWmQYvH_BGWWxrMFKMg","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"282","text":"• Vacunas: neumococo, influenza, SARS-CoV-2, VRS.","guid":"ln8Ynr7uHJadxyAchfU6-w","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"282","text":"• Higiene oral: cepillado dental diario y cuidados dentales.","guid":"kQKz0eeeKyGy90BpNj-Zvw","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"282","text":"• Tratamiento de enfermedades cardíacas y pulmonares subyacentes.","guid":"kgF_xTN4vXNJKf6n0FczWQ","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"282","text":"• Terapia de deglución en casos de aspiración (ej. masticar bien,\\Ncomidas pequeñas, postura adecuada).","guid":"FMK4Kbkh0NIEXAnhMlaARg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":287,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"NAC JAMA-2024","id":"map_1166","resolved_references":[]}